### ============================================================
### Jobs V2 — Time Management / Scheduled Jobs
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### All endpoints require MaintenanceRole.
###
### Known jobs (registered at startup):
###   - PaymentWindowExpiredJob     (Payments BC)
###   - StockAdjustmentJob          (Inventory BC)
###   - SoftReservationExpiredJob   (Presale BC)
###   - CurrencyRateSyncTask        (Currencies BC)
###   - PaymentWindowTimeoutJob     (Inventory BC)
###   - SnapshotOrderItemsJob       (Orders BC)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# JOBS
# ============================================================

### Get all registered jobs and their current status
# Expected: 200 OK  →  List<JobStatusSummary>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get deferred job queue (jobs waiting to be picked up)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  List<DeferredJobQueueVm>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/deferred
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get execution history for PaymentWindowExpiredJob
# Expected: 200 OK  →  List<JobExecutionRecord>
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/PaymentWindowExpiredJob/history?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get history — StockAdjustmentJob
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/StockAdjustmentJob/history?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get history — CurrencyRateSyncTask
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/CurrencyRateSyncTask/history?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get history — SoftReservationExpiredJob
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/SoftReservationExpiredJob/history?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Enable a job (e.g. after it was disabled)
# Expected: 200 OK
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/PaymentWindowExpiredJob/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Disable a job (e.g. for maintenance)
# Expected: 200 OK
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/StockAdjustmentJob/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Register a new custom job
# Schedule: standard cron expression (5-part)
# Expected: 200 OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/register
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "jobName": "MyCustomJob",
  "schedule": "0 */6 * * *",
  "timeZoneId": "Europe/Warsaw",
  "maxRetries": 3
}
###

### Register job — every minute (for testing)
# Expected: 200 OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs/register
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "jobName": "TestHeartbeatJob",
  "schedule": "* * * * *",
  "timeZoneId": null,
  "maxRetries": 1
}
###

### Unauthorized — no token
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/jobs
###
